{"tid":1567360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運動歌曲要夠氣勢！","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:05:25.000Z","uid":296509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f37eb9c3a798126f9c5cbd7eb64d509b2e4fb924","tid":1567360,"uid":296509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:01:20.000Z","msg":"唔知大家覺唔覺得《願榮光歸香港》其實唔夠氣勢？<br />\n除文宣以外，歌曲係非常重要，可以團結人心，建立民族意識。但個人就覺得依家首歌未夠氣勢，比較柔軟。<br />\n<br />\n聽返Do You Hear The People Sing，氣勢要強，激起士氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PUlQNsl4Qvk?list=FL5AX2yxsFshuwWKmG8ePWgw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPUlQNsl4Qvk%3Flist%3DFL5AX2yxsFshuwWKmG8ePWgw&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=dbcc9819\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PUlQNsl4Qvk?list=FL5AX2yxsFshuwWKmG8ePWgw</a><br />\n<br />\n再來一首來自 &quot;The Sum of All Fears 驚天核網&quot; 電影中的The Star-Spangled Banner<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5jIpAeYwPo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJ5jIpAeYwPo&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=dd5eb4ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J5jIpAeYwPo</a><br />\n<br />\n並非說《願榮光歸香港》不好，但對於運動推進，前線義士，一首氣勢強勁的歌曲更能聚集力量。<span style=\"color: red;\">《願榮光歸香港》比較像和理非，勇武或需另一首較激昂的歌曲。</span><br />\n純粹個人意見，不喜勿插，無意貶低任何歌曲創作。"},{"pid":"88e9c7c08c3dd8e8e5aa76aaf6de443305944ce9","tid":1567360,"uid":64226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"邊方面唔夠氣勢？樓主係睇曲定睇詞？"},{"pid":"c806aa77f0a473e248a878f1374a960cf9d3e8dc","tid":1567360,"uid":296509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88e9c7c08c3dd8e8e5aa76aaf6de443305944ce9","tid":1567360,"uid":64226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"邊方面唔夠氣勢？樓主係睇曲定睇詞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"主要是曲，節奏也是屬於柔軟<br />\n當然是屬個人意見啦"}]}